      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "A Caesarean section, or C-section, is a surgical procedure used to deliver
    a baby through an incision made in the mother\u2019s abdomen and uterus.\n\nIn
    this simulation, you will learn the key stages of the procedure in a safe and
    interactive environment.\n\nThe Patient View explains what happens during the
    surgery in simple terms and helps patients understand the process.\r\n \nThe
    Surgeon View focuses on the clinical steps and anatomical structures involved
    in performing the operation.\r\n\nPress Next to continue."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
